des: Planning to visit Tampa. Use this app to visit top 5 attractions and do the top five things while there. Don't miss out on what Tampa has to offer. Start by asking 'Alexa open Tampa guide' and follow it up by saying 'Help' to know sample commands you can say. This app also provides you with local news option
